[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0751","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0751.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0501","title":"Unix 账号弱口令漏洞","description":"Unix 系统账户存在可被猜测的弱口令漏洞。系统管理员或用户在创建账户时未设置足够复杂的密码（如空密码、默认密码或字典单词），导致攻击者可通过暴力破解、字典攻击或在线密码猜测等方式，在本地或远程登录场景下利用弱口令成功登录目标系统，获得未授权的 shell 访问权限。该漏洞影响所有 Unix 及类 Unix 操作系统（包括 Linux、BSD、Solaris 等），CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。修复建议为实施强密码策略和账户锁定机制。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0501"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-06-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:31.853","remediation":"在 /etc/pam.d/ 中配置 pam_cracklib.so 或 pam_pwquality.so 强制密码长度≥8位、含大小写字母和数字，并设置密码有效期≤90天；使用 `passwd -l` 锁定无密码账户，定期用 John the Ripper 审计弱口令；禁用不安全的 DES 加密，改用 SHA-512 密码哈希（`pwconv` 配合 `authconfig` 配置）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0501"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0751.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0762","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0762.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0508","title":"多款网络设备默认口令漏洞","description":"路由器、防火墙或其他网络设备的系统账户存在默认、空值或缺失密码的安全缺陷。攻击者可利用该漏洞通过默认凭据或空密码直接登录设备管理接口，获取未授权访问权限，进而完全控制受影响设备。此漏洞影响多种开源路由器及网络设备，CVSS评分4.6，危害等级中危。建议管理员立即修改默认账户密码或禁用不必要的默认账户以进行修复。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0508"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-06-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:32.663","remediation":"立即为所有网络设备（路由器、防火墙、VPN 网关等）的本地管理账户设置强密码（≥8 位，含大小写字母、数字及特殊字符），禁用或删除所有默认/预置账户（如 admin/root/guest），并启用账户锁定策略防止暴力破解。建议通过配置管理工具（如 Ansible）批量巡检全网设备的口令合规性。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0508"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0762.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0504","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0504.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0303","title":"BNU UUCP 后台程序缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"BNU UUCP 守护进程（uucpd）在处理超长主机名时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的主机名字符串触发该漏洞，导致服务进程崩溃或执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 OpenBSD 及其他运行 BNU UUCP 组件的系统，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0303"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-05-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:06.610","remediation":"立即升级 OpenBSD 至 2.3 及以上版本，或安装对应安全补丁。如 UUCP 服务非必需，在 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释 uucpd 行并重启 inetd 服务以禁用该守护进程。同时建议在主机层面通过防火墙限制对 TCP 540 端口的访问，仅允许可信主机通信。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0303"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0504.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0146","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0146.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0055","title":"Sun libnsl 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 操作系统的 libnsl（网络服务库）存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，漏洞源于对 RPC 请求参数长度缺乏正确的边界检查。本地或远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 RPC 数据包触发该漏洞，成功利用后可获得系统的 root 权限，完全控制受影响主机。该漏洞影响 Sun Solaris 2.x 系列版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0055"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-05-14T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:28.320","remediation":"立即为 Sun Solaris 安装 Sun Security Bulletin #00172 对应补丁，为 AIX 系统安装 APAR IX80543 修复程序。如无法立即打补丁，可通过限制本地用户登录、移除不可信用户访问权限、对关键系统启用强制访问控制机制（如 SELinux）作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/172","http://www-1.ibm.com/support/search.wss?rs=0&q=IX80543&apar=only"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0146.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0272","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0272.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0126","title":"SGI IRIX xterm 缓冲区溢出本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 及 Solaris 5.5.1 X11R6.3 系统中 xterm 终端模拟器与 Xaw 部件库存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向 xterm 的 `-xrm` 参数传递超长资源字符串触发缓冲区溢出，成功利用后可获得目标系统的 root 权限。该漏洞要求攻击者拥有本地账号，攻击复杂度较低，影响 SGI IRIX 和 Solaris 等 UNIX 系统的 X11R6.3 环境。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0126"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-05-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:38.733","remediation":"移除 xterm 的 SUID 权限位：`chmod u-s /usr/bin/X11/xterm`，防止本地用户通过 `-xrm` 参数以 root 权限执行任意代码。同时升级 Solaris 至 5.5.1 以上补丁版本，或从 IRIX 厂商处获取 xterm 安全修补程序。如不使用 Xaw 库程序，建议将其一并移除或降权。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-010.shtml","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/338","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0126.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0126","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0126.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0126.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0126.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0126.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83078/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154100_154200.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--160f8a79-d4d5-4c33-8fab-f1a31520e3d2.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0272.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0247","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0247.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0108","title":"SGI IRIX 6.3 xrm 本地缓冲区溢出权限提升漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.3 操作系统的 printers 程序中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向 xrm 组件提交特制的输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，导致以 root 权限执行任意代码，从而完全控制目标系统。该漏洞仅需本地用户权限即可利用，影响 SGI IRIX 6.3 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0108"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-05-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:36.280","remediation":"升级 SGI IRIX 至 6.4 及以上版本，或安装 SGI 提供的补丁程序。作为临时缓解措施，限制对受影响系统的本地访问权限，仅授权可信用户使用，并移除 setuid 权限位。鉴于 IRIX 已停止维护，建议迁移至受支持的操作系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://seclists.org/bugtraq/1997/May/191","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19267","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0108.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0108","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0108.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0108.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0108.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0108.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83064/info.html","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--0828884e-fed7-43ba-9578-192236803d75.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/e7bd3e92452a8dc8da42d94ae3ba208936d5a5b9/1999.tsv","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0247.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0170","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0170.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0069","title":"Sun Solaris ufsdump/ufsrestore 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Solaris 7.0 系统中的 ufsdump/ufsrestore 工具存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，拥有本地访问权限的攻击者可通过向该工具传递特制参数触发溢出，覆盖内存数据，进而实现权限提升或以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Solaris 7.0 版本，CVSS 评分 8.4，危害等级高危，需系统本地账号方可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":8.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0069"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-04-29T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:30.363","remediation":"升级 Solaris 系统至 Solaris 8 及以上版本，或安装 Sun 官方补丁 106880-01 (SPARC) / 106881-01 (x86)。临时缓解措施：限制 ufsdump/ufsrestore 的 setuid 权限，仅授权管理用户执行文件系统备份操作。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/169","http://www.osvdb.org/8158","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19534","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0069.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0069","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/f06304a9243ce013bfbf7cea427539f6409c0a05/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0069.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0069.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0069.md","https://github.com/krafthack-by-techday/Night-s-watch/blob/30ae1bcc335306fe4c5507b2c629cae4932e515e/cve/nvd/CVE-1999-0069_0f0c3530-7572-4860-a943-991d78115c24","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-xqg2-r5rv-62x6/GHSA-xqg2-r5rv-62x6.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0069.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0170.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0170.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0170.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0398","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0398.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0212","title":"Sun Solaris rpc.mountd 错误信息泄露漏洞","description":"Solaris/SunOS 系统中 RPC 服务 rpc.mountd 存在信息泄露漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 RPC 请求触发该服务返回详细错误信息，从而枚举服务器上的文件系统结构和文件是否存在。该漏洞影响 Solaris 及 SunOS 多个版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，为后续攻击收集目标信息。官方已发布安全补丁修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0212"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-04-29T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:55.403","remediation":"安装 Sun Security Bulletin #168 (1998年发布) 对应的操作系统补丁，更新至已修复该问题的 Solaris 版本。如无法打补丁，可在 /etc/hosts.deny 中添加 \"mountd: ALL\" 并用 /etc/hosts.allow 按需放行可信主机，同时在防火墙上限制对 rpc.mountd (端口 2049 及 rpcbind 端口 111) 的访问。若不需要 NFS 服务，可停止并禁用 mountd 服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/168","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/i-048.shtml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0398.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0030","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0030.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0009","title":"ISC BIND 反向查询远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"ISC BIND（Berkeley Internet Name Domain）4.9 及 8.x 版本存在反向查询缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标 DNS 服务器发送特制的反向查询请求，触发缓冲区溢出，导致拒绝服务或任意代码执行。该漏洞影响运行 BIND 4.9 及 8.x 的多种操作系统平台，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。厂商建议立即升级至不受影响的版本。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0009"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-04-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:20.137","remediation":"立即升级 BIND 至 8.2 或更高版本，或在条件允许时迁移至 BIND 9 系列（如 9.3.0+），因为 8.2 已修复逆查询缓冲区溢出漏洞。如无法立即升级，可在 named.conf 中禁用 `inverse-query` 选项以临时缓解风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/180","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/134","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9808-083","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19112","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0009.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0009","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0009.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0009.md","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/252.txt","https://github.com/demisto/content/blob/710308a4be78e89bc993b4d594b444aeb805b7d8/Packs/McAfeeNSM/Integrations/McAfeeNSMv2/README.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-p4fw-6pfr-4xqr/GHSA-p4fw-6pfr-4xqr.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0009.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/deleted.rules","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/B/bind_iquery.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0030.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0044","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0044.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0010","title":"ISC BIND 4.9/8 DNS Message 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"ISC BIND 4.9 及 8 版本中的 DNS 消息处理组件存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标服务器发送特制的恶意 DNS 查询消息，利用消息解析过程中的缺陷触发服务崩溃，导致 DNS 服务不可用。该漏洞影响大量使用上述版本 BIND 的 DNS 服务器，攻击者通过发送精心构造的 DNS 请求报文即可实施攻击，无需复杂前置条件。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0010"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-04-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:20.340","remediation":"升级至 BIND 8.2 或更高版本以修复 DNS 消息解析缺陷；BIND 4.9/8 系列已停止维护，建议迁移至 BIND 9.x 系列并升级到 ISC 发布的最新稳定版（如 9.18.x 或 9.20.x）。如暂无法升级，应在边界防火墙上限制外部 DNS 查询来源 IP 并启用递归查询访问控制列表以降低攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9808-083"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0044.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0046","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0046.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0011","title":"ISC BIND 4.9/8 CNAME及区域传输拒绝服务漏洞","description":"ISC BIND 4.9 和 BIND 8 版本的域名解析服务存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者通过发送特制的 CNAME 资源记录或利用不规范的区域传输（Zone Transfer）请求，可导致目标 BIND 服务进程崩溃或资源耗尽，停止响应正常的域名解析请求。该漏洞影响广泛部署的 DNS 服务器，在无需认证的条件下即可触发，对网络基础设施的可用性构成直接威胁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0011"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-04-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:20.490","remediation":"立即升级 ISC BIND 至 8.2 及以上版本，推荐直接迁移至 BIND 9.x 系列。在 named.conf 中配置 allow-transfer 仅允许受信从服务器（如 allow-transfer { 192.168.1.2; };），并在面向不可信网络的接口上通过 allow-query 和 allow-recursion 限制查询来源。如无法立即升级，可在边界防火墙阻断外部对 TCP 53 端口的区域传输请求，并限制 UDP 53 的异常 CNAME 查询流量。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/180","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9808-083"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0046.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0373","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0373.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0190","title":"Sun Solaris rpcbind 任意文件写入漏洞","description":"Solaris 系统的 rpcbind 服务存在任意文件写入漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标系统的 rpcbind 服务发送特制 RPC 请求，利用符号链接或文件路径遍历等方式覆盖系统任意文件，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Solaris 操作系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。建议及时安装对应安全补丁进行修复。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0190"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-04-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:49.320","remediation":"立即应用 Sun Security Bulletin #167 提供的补丁程序，或升级到 Solaris 7 及以上版本。作为临时缓解措施，在 /etc/hosts.deny 中添加 ALL:ALL 限制 rpcbind 访问，并在防火墙上仅允许受信任网络访问 rpcbind 端口 111/TCP 和 111/UDP。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/167"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0373.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0456","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0456.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0270","title":"SGI IRIX Performer API Search Tool 目录遍历漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 操作系统自带的 Performer API Search Tool 中的 pfdispaly.cgi 脚本存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向 CGI 程序发送包含特殊路径序列（如 ../）的恶意 HTTP 请求，突破 Web 根目录限制，读取服务器上任意文件，包括 /etc/passwd 等敏感系统文件。该漏洞影响安装了 performer_tools 组件的 SGI IRIX 系统，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。厂商已发布安全公告建议禁用相关 CGI 脚本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0270"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-04-03T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:02.600","remediation":"建议立即升级 SGI Performer API Search Tool 至最新补丁版本，或从 Web 服务器中移除 pfdispaly.cgi 脚本。如无法升级，可在 Web 服务器配置中限制对 pfdispaly.cgi 的访问（如禁用该 CGI 执行权限、限制访问来源 IP），并部署 Web 应用防火墙拦截目录遍历攻击载荷。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/i-041.shtml","http://www.osvdb.org/134","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/64","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/810","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0270.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0270.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0270","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0270.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0270.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/2d2ea2d13a3a7facfa195486d4f9782c62a06518/1999/CVE-1999-0270.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/1b69cf2313f68e29acceed58f52f6109cd37bb04/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-02xx/CVE-1999-0270.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0270.json","https://github.com/CyberSecAI/cve_info/blob/03b7e36424574a3a9ba5fd13480a326b666a1046/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0270.json","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelist-dev/blob/5b8fbb570438e8094550205589cc6f1d122acc94/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0270.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0456.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0015","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0015.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0003","title":"Common Desktop Environment ToolTalk RPC 服务缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"ToolTalk 数据库服务器（rpc.ttdbserverd）存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证，通过向目标系统发送特制请求即可触发缓冲区溢出，从而以 root 权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Xi Graphics Maximum CDE 1.2.3、TriTeal TED CDE 4.3 及 Sun Solaris 2.5.1 等系统，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，属于当年最具破坏力的远程代码执行漏洞之一。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0003"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:18.353","remediation":"立即禁用 rpc.ttdbserverd 服务（进程名：rpc.ttdbserverd），执行 /usr/bin/killall rpc.ttdbserverd 终止进程，并从 /etc/inetd.conf（或 /etc/xinetd.d/）中注释 rstatd/rusersd 相关行后重启 inetd。对于 SGI IRIX，应安装 SGI 安全公告 19981101-01 中提供的补丁。对于 Sun Solaris 系统，应用 Sun 提供的对应安全补丁（如 SunOS 5.5.1 相关补丁）。上述操作系统均已终止安全支持，强烈建议迁移至受支持的现代操作系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/122","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19102","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0003.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0003.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0003","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0003.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/572.txt","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0003.md","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/rpc.rules","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0003.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8954696320cbff8f7d95f98854cf0e72222fc646/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-gxwg-52wj-vc7w/GHSA-gxwg-52wj-vc7w.json","https://github.com/FIRSTdotorg/Vuln4Cast/blob/c93910d268aa5b5d2260adb9b5d92094b2d06daf/YearlyVuln4Cast-V1.ipynb"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0015.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0229","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0229.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0098","title":"Sendmail SMTP HELO 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Sendmail SMTP 服务在处理 HELO 命令时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标服务器的 25 端口发送特制的 HELO 请求触发该漏洞，成功利用可导致任意代码执行或服务崩溃，攻击者借此可完全控制服务器或隐藏恶意活动痕迹。该漏洞影响多个版本的 Sendmail，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0098"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:34.903","remediation":"立即升级 Sendmail 至 8.9.0 或更高版本（该版本修复了 SMTP HELO 命令缓冲区溢出问题）。SLMail 用户应升级至 3.0 及以上版本，Mercury Mail Server 用户升级至最新版本。如无法立即升级，可在防火墙层面限制 SMTP（TCP 25）端口仅允许可信来源访问，同时在 Sendmail 配置中限制 HELO 命令输入长度作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0098"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0229.toml"}]